item.title: Aspose.OMR for Java 19.12 Release Notes
item.description: This page contains release notes information for Aspose.OMR for Java 19.12 First Public Release of Aspose.OMR for Java We are pleased to announce the first public release of Aspose.OMR for Java. It is simple to use API that allows developers to perform OMR operation on images. Aspose.OMR can perform OMR operation on JPEG, PNG, GIF, TIFF, and BMP image files and save the output in CSV and JSON formats.
